\v 11 meinai to yermam…ô k…®rik r…®p…ôh n…®vhir…ôk…®nien n…®hu nim…ô k…®rik m…®n yame ror p…®s…®n ye n…®hu nim…ô yame kw…ôvhir…ôk…®n ta, yame in e Yesu Kristo.\x - \xo 3:11 \xt Aes 28:16; 1 Pita 2:4-6 \x*
