\v 11 In e n…ôfrak…®sien mu…ô meriaji-p…ô taktakun m…®ne, n…®kumh…ô ram…ôs …ômaw…ô; k…®ni yaks…ôkwakw…ô, k…®ni yakamhav…ôn ye neip…ôn m…ôt…®t, narmam…ô kamhauh …ômaw…ô, k…®ni kap…ômaw…ô nim…ô r…®k…ôk.\x - \xo 4:11 \xt 2 Kor 11:23-27 \x*
